Hm, I wonder what this large metal door is hiding... 
It won't budge.

There a bit of a crack in the door I can
see through, at least.
Guess I won't have to wonder for long.
Let's see what secrets you hide...
WHAT DO YOU MEAN JAMIE IS HERE!?
Isn't it your job or something to keep him safe?

What do YOU think is going to happen when he tries to
explore that hallway a bit further? It never ends!

Is that really what you want to happen to him? 
For him to get lost in endless doors?
We can't even know what's behind every single door, 
it would require a manual check of each one!
Who has the time to do that!?
